{{Refimprove|date = March 2009}} The '''KAIROS Prize''' has been awarded to European artists and scholars from the fields of visual and performing arts, music, architecture, design, film, photography, literature and journalism since 2007 by the [[Alfred Toepfer Stiftung F.V.S.|Alfred Toepfer Foundation]] in Hamburg. It is endowed with a sum of 75,000 Euro.<ref>{{cite web|url = http://toepfer-stiftung.de/kairos-preis/|title= KAIROS-Preis|publisher= Alfred Toepfer Stiftung F.V.S.|accessdate = 30 January 2015}}</ref>
