{{Infobox music festival | image = | music_festival_name = Kao nekad pred Božić | location = [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | years_active = 1999 – present | dates = 6 December | organiser = | genre = [[Christmas carols]], [[Christmas music]] | website = }} '''Kao nekad pred Božić''' (English: As it used to be before Christmas) is an annual one-day [[christmas music]] [[festival]] held in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://avaz.ba/vijesti/bih/324621/18-festival-bozicnih-pjesama-narodnih-igara-i-obicaja-kao-nekad-pred-bozic-2017%E2%80%9C|title=18. festival božićnih pjesama, narodnih igara i običaja 'Kao nekad pred Božić 2017“|publisher=avaz.ba}}</ref> It was established in 1999 as a joint venture by [[Croatia|Croatian]] and [[Catholic]] cultural and religious organizations in Bosnia and Herzegovina. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://depo.ba/clanak/169624/kao-nekad-pred-bozic-2017-18-festival-bozicnih-pjesama-narodnih-igara-i-obicaja|title=Kao nekad pred Božić 2017: 18. festival božićnih pjesama, narodnih igara i običaja |publisher=depo.ba}}</ref> The founders include [[HKD Napredak]], the [[Franciscan Province of Bosna Srebrena]] and others. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.doznajemo.com/post/festival-kao-nekad-pred-bozic-ove-godine-06.12.2017.-u-dvorani-dom-mladih-u-sarajevu|title=Festival Kao nekad pred Božić ove godine u Domu mladih|publisher=doznajemo.com}}</ref> The festival is held in the [[Dom Mladih]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bljesak.info/kultura/flash/u-sarajevu-odrzan-festival-bozicnih-pjesama-narodnih-igara-i-obicaja/140658|title=U Sarajevu održan festival božićnih pjesama, narodnih igara i običaja|publisher=bljesak.info}}</ref> It hosts numerous renowned church choirs, folklore groups and contemporary pop musicians. Guests and performers have included [[Goran Karan]], [[Oliver Dragojević]], [[Dražen Žerić]], [[Klapa s Mora]], [[Rajko Dujmić]] and others. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.oslobodjenje.ba/o2/kultura/muzika/kao-nekad-pred-bozic-blagdanska-atmosfera-u-domu-mladih|title=Kao nekad pred Božić: Blagdanska atmosfera u Domu mladih|publisher=oslobodjenje.ba}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.doznajemo.com/post/festival-kao-nekad-pred-bozic-ove-godine-06.12.2017.-u-dvorani-dom-mladih-u-sarajevu|title=Festival Kao nekad pred Božić ove godine u Domu mladih|publisher=doznajemo.com}}</ref>
Apart from hosting a large christmas music concert, the festival also hosts numerous folklore and cultural groups that present traditional folk dances and [[Kolo (dance)|kolo]]s from Bosnia and Herzegovina, Croatia and the diaspora. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fokus.ba/vijesti/kultura/festival-kao-nekad-pred-bozic-2017-u-sarajevu/916219/|title=Festival “Kao nekad pred Božić 2017” u Sarajevu|publisher=fokus.ba}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://dnevni-list.ba/festival-kao-nekad-pred-bozic-2017/|title=Festival “Kao nekad pred Božić 2017”|publisher=dnevni-list.ba}}</ref>
